Class CircleFinderThread

  • java.lang.Object
    • craj.mapDigesterLocator.GenericObservable<java.util.List<CircleFinding>>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MapDigesterCircleFinderThread

    public abstract class CircleFinderThread
extends GenericObservable<java.util.List<CircleFinding>>
implements java.lang.Runnable
    Searches in a given image-file for circles. This abstract class implements no search algorithm but defines the interface for the calculation-method findCircleCoordinates and the functionality to notify all observers observing this object with the found circle-data. After an implementation of the findCircleCoordinates completed, the returning circle findings are available as an argument in the observers update-method.
